- Technical Details
    - Tech Stack:
        - HTML, React via CDN (UMD), in-browser Babel, vanilla CSS
        - site_kit (via https://k1monfared.github.io/site_kit/) for chrome
        - JSON schemas for data validation
    - Key Files:
        - index.html: app shell, loads React + Babel
        - app.jsx: single-file SPA, hash-routed
        - licenses/index.json: catalog
        - licenses/<id>/{meta,features,analysis}.json + text.raw.txt + text.html
        - schemas/*.schema.json + feature-vocabulary.json
        - .claude/skills/{lookup-license,extract-features,deep-analysis}/
        - .claude/commands/{add-license,backfill-feature,refresh-analysis}/
    - Architecture Notes:
        - Static site, no build step; deployable directly to GH Pages from master
        - All UI state in URL (filter set, compare set, column order)
        - Citation model: sentence IDs (s-N) stable across re-runs, linked via CSS :target highlight
        - Feature vocabulary drives comparison table rows; licenses render not_assessed for vocabulary keys they haven't filled in yet

